OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother hot day with
OL,6,Ftemperatures continuing to rise. Dry
OL,7,Fand sunny with light winds, but breezy
OL,8,Falong the coast where temperatures
OL,9,Fcould be a degree or two cooler.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and settled evening
OL,12,Fwith clear skies across the whole
OL,13,Fregion. Winds will be light and
OL,14,Fvariable. Remaining mild overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FLargely bright and sunny
OL,17,Fthroughout. Light and variable winds
OL,18,Fbut breezy along the coast, Feeling
OL,19,Fhot inland but slightly cooler along
OL,20,Fthe coast in the breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
