OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FLargely bright and sunny throughout,
OL,7,Fand notably hot on Tuesday.
OL,8,FTemperatures may start to decrease
OL,9,Fslightly from Wednesday and into
OL,10,FThursday as it becomes breezier,
OL,11,Fespecially along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
